high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the stove
Pick up the pan from the front left stove burner
Turn around and walk over to the round white table
Put the pan down on the table
Pick up the large spoon with black handle from the table
Put the spoon in the pan on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the large spoon in the pan on the table

high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the counter and walk to the stove on the right.
Pick up the pan from the front right corner of the stove.
Turn around, hang a right just past the counter and turn left at the wall to face the round white table.
Put the pan on the left side of the table behind the bottle.
Pick up the spoon with the black handle in between the salt shakers on the right side of the table.
Put the spoon inside the pan on the left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a spoon on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and go straight, past the kitchen counter, to go to the stove ahead.
Pick up the pan nearest to you on the stove.
Turn right and step forward, then turn right and go across the room, turn right past the kitchen counter, go to the wall, then turn left to face the white table.
Put the pan on the white table.
Pick up the large spoon on the table.
Put the large spoon on the pan.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a large spoon in it on the white table.
